to dogs and horses.

248
00:24:40,762 --> 00:24:42,252
Right.

249
00:24:43,965 --> 00:24:45,933
You rock!

250
00:25:04,753 --> 00:25:06,482
Hello?

251
00:25:08,356 --> 00:25:09,789
<i>-Libby?
-Henry.</i>

252
00:25:09,958 --> 00:25:13,394
-ls she there? ls she all right?
-Yeah, she's here.

253
00:25:14,229 --> 00:25:17,494
