361
00:35:42,890 --> 00:35:44,380
Thank you, London!

362
00:35:49,697 --> 00:35:53,098
l say, are you all right?
Are you sure?

363
00:35:54,969 --> 00:35:58,029
-What a disgrace!
-Must be American.

364
00:35:59,307 --> 00:36:02,708
